  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3 re-evaluation)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. This re-evaluation elevates the Model Risk Level to 3 following a regulatory query regarding broader clinical deployment scope. Thirteen credibility factors are addressed; twelve are fully assessed and meet or exceed required levels. The Equivalency of input parameters factor is documented as not requiring assessment because the validation experiments were conducted on the same hardware configuration as the COU device — however, this rationale has not been formally adjudicated and the factor carries factorStatus 'not-assessed' rather than 'not-applicable', leaving a material gap at MRL 3.",
