      "rationale": "NIH predictions compared against bench measurements at all 5 operating points. Mean absolute error 6.8%; maximum 9.4%. All predictions fall within expanded uncertainty interval (k=2). Validation metric u_val computed per ASME V&V 20. Required level met."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the quantities of interest",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
