      "acceptanceCriteria": "Primary QoI (NIH/RH index) must be directly relevant to the clinical decision and mapped to the acceptance criterion RH < 1.",
      "rationale": "NIH is the established hemolysis surrogate for CPB devices per FDA guidance. The relative hemolysis index RH = NIH_device/NIH_predicate is the direct acceptance criterion. QoI relevance confirmed by clinical advisory review. Required level met."
    },
