      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence demonstrated; residuals reduced by at least 4 orders of magnitude and monitored QoI stable over final 500 iterations.",
      "rationale": "All steady-state simulations converged to residuals below 1e-5 for continuity and momentum. NIH monitor value stable to <0.1% over final 500 iterations. Convergence plots archived in simulation log. Required level met."
