      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Biological variability in blood samples characterized; minimum 3 independent blood donations used per operating point.",
      "rationale": "Validation experiments used pooled bovine blood from 4 independent donations per operating point. Inter-donation variability in baseline plasma free hemoglobin documented (CV 8.3%). Sample preparation per ASTM F1841 confirmed. Required level met."
